log_line_prefix = '%t [%p]: db=%d,user=%u,app=%a,client=%h '
2026-01-03 08:21:34 IST [2466]: db=postgres,user=postgres,app=psql,client=[local] LOG:  statement: select * from emp;

Rotation example.,
-------------------
find . -name ".zip" -mtime +90days {rm -rf}
find . -name ".log" -mtime +5days {gzip *}

